Caribbean Radio Lighthouse

[

The Caribbean Radio Lighthouse is a Christian radio station broadcasting to the islands of the Caribbean from the island of Antigua on 1160 AM and 92.3 FM.

]

In 1972, in response to requests from Caribbean pastors and missionaries, the Lord led Dr. Tom Freeney, General Director of Baptist International Missions, Inc., to suggest that a Christian radio station be built on Antigua.
